Package: Rdashscope
Type: Package
Title: Vendor-Agnostic LLM Chat Client for R (OpenAI-Compatible) with Single-Cell Friendly Formatters
Version: 0.2.3
Authors@R: c(
    person("Your", "Name", email = "you@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Lightweight R client for calling OpenAI-compatible Chat Completions APIs from multiple vendors
    by specifying api_key, base_url, and model. Includes class-aware input formatters for single-cell workflows
    (e.g., compact Seurat summaries), plus singleAsk() and multiAsk() helpers for one-shot and multi-turn chats.
